==Product form==

This is the application of products, it can add, modify and view all product data classified in different tabs: main data, attachments, data on the registry modifications and assignments to folders.

===Product Details Tab===

In this tab you can view and modify the main product data. Here we relate all information fields.

[productos-formulario.png]

- **Name (*):** Name given to the product.
- **Ref.:** Internal reference product
- **Description:** Description of the product.
- **Price (€) (*):** Product price before applying tax.
- **Extra. (%):** Discount carried out in this product.
- **VAT rate (%):** VAT to be applied to the purchase.
- **Dimensions:** Physical Dimensions of the product.
- **Weight:** Total weight of the product.
- **Web:** Product web tab.
- **Volume:** Total volume of the product.
- **Current photo:** Current image of the product.
- **New photo:** To change the image of the product.


(*) **Required when creating or modifying a product fields.**

